# Production API origin the built SPA calls. Leave empty to use same-origin "/api"
# (e.g. when the SPA is served behind a reverse proxy that forwards /api to the API).
# In local dev this is ignored — Vite proxies /api to the backend (see vite.config.ts).
VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Optional: override the dev proxy target if the API runs somewhere other than http://localhost:5002
# VITE_DEV_API_TARGET=http://localhost:5002
